     And now for something completely different ...

     To make this European-meeting of FidoNet participants more
     attractive, we've taken the initiative to organize parallel to
     EUROCON-IV another international event.

     Whereas EUROCON looks more at the political and organizational
     point of view of communicating in our net, TECHCON-I will be
     THE thing not to miss if you're interested in the technical
     aspects of our pass-time.

     We believe a very good programme is being put together, the
     main items are being listed below, though proper scheduling
     over the two days still has to take place :

               * V42/V42bis
               * FTSC
               * European Standards
               * Virus
               * Data-compression
               * New products
               * FidoNet Compatible Architecture
               * Mailers
               * Fido-software for non-IBM PC's
               * Message-fossils

     Apart from this we are trying to organize, as part of
     TECHCON-I, a mystery-event which at this time we are still
     calling

                    "The clash of the titans"

     Further announcements on this will follow later ...


